data.description: Welcome to this stunning brick-front residence boasting four spacious bedrooms and three baths. Nestled on a picturesque corner lot, this home exudes charm and elegance. Step inside to discover a grand primary suite featuring a separate sitting room, perfect for relaxation or unwinding after a long day. Upstairs, you'll find a versatile space ideal for an office or recreational area. Entertain guests in style with formal living and dining rooms, or gather around the cozy fireplace in the sunken family room. The expansive kitchen, complete with a breakfast area, is a chef's dream, offering ample space for culinary creativity. Convenient features include a side-entry garage and abundant storage throughout. Nice sized fully fenced yard is perfect for entertaining. Enjoy the convenience of being close to Stonecrest Mall, while also relishing the privacy of this corner lot gem. Recent upgrades include new luxury vinyl plank flooring in the kitchen, ensuring both style and durability. Rest easy knowing that the roof is just two years old. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional home yours. Schedule a showing today!
